  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为GradeSync系统设计一个故障注入测试的序列图，核心场景是验证ESP32控制器在SPI通信异常时的容错能力。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ESP32 Controller",
        "Target Subsystem",
        "SPI Fault Frame"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是本地机器发起测试，ESP32作为中间层向目标子系统发送SPI帧？我需要确认参与者的层级关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Local Machine",
        "ESP32 Controller",
        "Target Subsystem"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Local Machine是测试设计端，ESP32是执行代理。目标子系统收到帧后，要交给FaultManager做状态校验。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FaultManager",
        "State Mask",
        "Validate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把前四个参与者排好：Local Machine、ESP32 Controller、Target Subsystem、FaultManager。然后画出设计故障注入活动到SPI帧发送的流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Local Machine",
        "ESP32 Controller",
        "Target Subsystem",
        "FaultManager",
        "Design Fault Injection Campaign",
        "SPI Fault Frame"
